Code preview of the table teacherinfo

drop table if exists teacherinfo;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: teacherinfo */
/*==============================================================*/
create table teacherinfo
(
id varchar(20) not null comment '账户主键',
real_name varchar(10) comment '真实姓名',
work_experience varchar(100) comment '工作经历',
study_experience varchar(100) comment '学习经历',
accademic_title varchar(100) comment '职称',
university varchar(10) comment '所属大学的名称',
employeenum varchar(20) comment '工号',
primary key (id)
);

alter table teacherinfo comment '这是用来存储身份为教师的用户的个人身份信息';

alter table teacherinfo add constraint FK_Reference_2 foreign key (id)
references account (id) on delete restrict on update restrict;
